1
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,480
Zhou Yi.

2
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,080
Zhou Yi.

3
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,200
Zhou Yi.

4
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:27,960
You're here.

5
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,120
Dude.

6
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,000
You getting addicted to hitting me?

7
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,280
You...

8
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,600
You moonlighting here too?

9
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,480
This is my full-time job.

10
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:48,040
I told you last time, I work next door.

11
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,200
This is what I do.

12
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,800
Yin-Realm Exorcism.

13
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,600
Same idea as collecting these bills.

14
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,720
Liu Liu said

15
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,400
every time you

16
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,120
do that kind of thing,

17
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,000
you get sick.

18
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:06,920
How are you doing?

19
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,680
Sit, sit, sit.

20
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,080
Have a seat.

21
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:14,400
Lin You,

22
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,320
let me tell you,

23
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,480
you really work wonders.

24
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,680
Before, every time I channeled someone,

25
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:19,960
even if I didn't get seriously sick,

26
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,520
I'd be bedridden for ten days or two weeks.

27
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,000
This time I just got a little cold.

28
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:25,840
Nothing serious at all.

29
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:30,480
Lin You,

30
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,240
you really are my Lucky Star.

31
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:34,960
With you around from now on,

32
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,360
I can definitely go back to Daji.

33
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:41,560
You said you lived at Daji until you were ten.

34
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,400
So the boss is your...?

35
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,400
Lao Wang?

36
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,280
He picked me up off the street.

37
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,680
After I turned ten,

38
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,520
Lao Wang stopped letting me get involved with Daji.

39
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,280
Why'd he dump you here?

40
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,800
I was born with a weak heart,

41
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,320
and my Empathic Ability is too strong.

42
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:01,760
I get sucked into the dead's minds too easily.

43
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,160
So he dumped me here to accumulate merit.

44
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,280
And this "dumping"

45
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,720
has gone on for over ten years.

46
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,720
He absolutely won't let me come back.

47
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,520
Lin You,

48
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,760
but it's different now.

49
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,760
With you, my Big Flashbang,

50
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,000
I can do whatever I want,

51
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,920
go wherever I want.

52
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,920
Where do you think you're going?

53
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,920
You little brat.

54
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,360
Brother Bai.

55
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,360
All better now, huh?

56
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,560
Where you running off to?

57
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,520
Where you going? Don't hit me!

58
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,200
Asking for a beating?

59
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,840
Lin You, Lin You, Lin You.

60
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,920
He's bringing in money.

61
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,080
Lin You.

62
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,600
Goofball.

63
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,880
Hi, hi, hi.

64
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,400
Liu Liu told me about you.

65
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:50,160
This young man looks...

66
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,240
Looking sharp!

67
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:52,560
Such a big guy.

68
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,800
Built tough.

69
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,040
So, how's it going?

70
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:59,360
You happy working at Daji?

71
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,680
No worries.

72
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,480
If not, you can come work for me.

73
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:08,760
I even offer insurance here.

74
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,920
Bai Meilan.

75
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,200
Just call me Brother Bai.

76
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,640
Goofball.

77
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,880
Don't mind him.

78
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,600
Just call me Sis.

79
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,560
Bai...

80
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,520
It's fine.

81
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,840
You'll get used to it.

82
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,360
This kid's pretty goofy.

83
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,600
Oh right, Lin You.

84
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,160
I actually need to talk to you.

85
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,840
About what?

86
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,560
Is it any of your business?

87
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,320
I...

88
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:44,960
Go on, get lost.

89
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,080
Go do some work over there.

90
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,560
Come, sit down.

91
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:50,760
Have a seat.

92
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,960
Listen, let me tell you.

93
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,720
Here's the thing.

94
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:54,520
I have a younger sister.

95
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,080
Lately,

96
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,240
weird things keep happening at her place.

97
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,880
Her neighbor's this crazy old lady.

98
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,600
That old lady is super creepy.

99
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,360
So I was thinking,

100
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,600
if you're free,

101
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,480
come check things out with me.

102
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,440
Sis Xiaobai,

103
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,920
Consider it done.

104
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,200
We're all family here.

105
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,000
Lin You,

106
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,840
let's go together.

107
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:14,680
Okay?

108
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:20,000
I'd have to discuss this with Liu Liu first.

109
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,240
Don't worry about that.

110
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,280
I just called Lao Wang this morning.

111
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,720
Liu Liu knows too.

112
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,080
That kid's a good one.

113
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,200
It's all good.

114
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,880
Just a little something from me.

115
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,360
It's not much.

116
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,400
Take it.

117
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,360
Wait, no.

118
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,280
This red envelope is...

119
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,880
This one's for Zhou Yi, this one's mine.

120
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:41,600
Brother Bai.

121
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,480
Call me Sis.

122
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,840
That's mine.

123
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,440
You're not going anywhere.

124
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,960
Let's go, go, go.

125
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,360
Brother Bai.

126
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,280
Sis.

127
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,360
Isn't this just a normal old building?

128
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,040
You'll find out once we go inside.

129
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,160
Come on, right here.

130
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,600
Here, have some fruit.

131
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:04,880
Xiao Bai.

132
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:05,920
This is Lin You.

133
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,320
I told him about your situation.

134
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,560
Had him come take a look for you.

135
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,240
Hello.

136
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,000
Sorry to intrude.

137
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,600
Not at all, Master Lin.

138
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,760
Sorry for the trouble.

139
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,080
Making a special trip out here.

140
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,600
Just call me Lin You.

141
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,040
Why so formal all of a sudden?

142
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,000
She insisted on bringing you something.

143
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,360
Xiao Bai.

144
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,680
Go ahead and tell Lin You.

145
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,360
What exactly happened at your place?

146
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,679
It started after I moved in.

147
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:55,840
Grandma,

148
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,520
What are you doing?

149
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,360
Burning paper in the hallway is so dangerous!

150
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:02,080
You'll start a fire.

151
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,480
Grandma,

152
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:20,640
make sure you put out the fire.

153
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,080
Just look at this hallway,

154
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,080
it's full of smoke.

155
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,720
That was just the beginning.

156
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,360
After that, strange things

157
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,800
just kept piling up.

158
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,040
Grandma, what are you doing?

159
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,680
I don't want this.

160
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,800
I don't want it!

161
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:25,680
Oh, right.

162
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,640
There's one more thing.

163
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,360
Since I've been pregnant,

164
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,000
I get hungry at night.

165
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,160
So I keep some

166
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,320
snacks and cookies at home.

167
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:41,360
But they seem to disappear way too fast.

168
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:45,240
I couldn't possibly eat that many alone.

169
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:48,120
At first,

170
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,200
I thought I was overthinking it.

171
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,480
Just my imagination.

172
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,120
But...

173
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,040
But then...

174
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,680
Until I saw it.

175
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:57,680
Saw what?

176
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,240
Here, take it slow.

177
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,440
This house...

178
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,320
my husband and I

179
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,760
saved up for years,

180
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,480
borrowed some from family,

181
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:42,040
and took a loan to buy it.

182
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:43,600
I mean, look at this mess.

183
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,240
We finally have a home,

184
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:47,600
and the baby's almost here.

185
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,480
I figured in a few years,

186
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,400
the kid could go to school right here.

187
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:51,640
Master Lin,

188
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:52,640
please help me out.

189
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,680
If there's no other way,

190
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:57,000
just help me sell it.

191
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,240
I'll take the loss.

192
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,120
Don't say that.

193
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,080
Xiao Bai, don't worry.

194
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,920
You're pregnant right now,

195
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,280
you can't let yourself get worked up.

196
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,800
Leave this to us.

197
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:09,120
I'll talk to Liu Liu when I get back.

198
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,120
She'll definitely have a solution.

199
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,960
You're due soon, right?

200
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,000
A little over a month to go.

201
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,840
I can tell it's a boy just by looking.

202
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,160
You can tell that?

203
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:25,480
Haven't seen a kid here since I moved in.

204
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,800
Things are gonna get lively now.

205
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:29,400
That old lady has no kids of her own.

206
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,840
You better stay away from her.

207
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,480
Even I get the creeps looking at her.

208
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,760
You're pretty far along now,

209
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:35,560
so you really need to be careful.

210
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:37,280
Thank you.

211
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:37,800
No problem.

212
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:38,560
I'll head off then.

213
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:39,280
Alright.

214
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,480
Lin You,

215
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,480
I'm not going back with you.

216
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,840
I'll take a walk with Xiao Bai,

217
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,040
get some sunshine and all.

218
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:45,720
Okay.

219
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:46,960
We'll be in touch then.

220
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:48,240
We'll get going.

221
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,240
See you.

222
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,320
Take it slow.

223
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:06,320
Lin You.

224
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:08,960
Tonight, grab your gear

225
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,760
and do a Stay-Over Investigation.

226
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,840
Why a Stay-Over again?

227
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:23,880
How about

228
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:27,200
we just let Yao Yao take a look?

229
00:13:31,680 --> 00:13:32,840
Sorry,

230
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:39,720
but I haven't seen Yao Yao in ages.

231
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:42,080
Just go already.

232
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:44,560
Didn't you already give

233
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,000
Sis Xiaobai your word?

234
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:50,760
How about

235
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:52,240
you come with me?

236
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,360
Me?

237
00:13:54,640 --> 00:13:55,240
No way.

238
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:59,440
My sister gave me her final warning.

239
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,880
If I go out late at night again,

240
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:02,120
she'll break my legs.

241
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,000
It's fine.

242
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,680
You're a Big Flashbang yourself.

243
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,600
Just go without a worry.

244
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:12,960
Besides,

245
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,200
whether that thing's even there

246
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,200
is anyone's guess.

247
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,400
Coffee?

248
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:32,200
What about Calming Tea?

249
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,120
Well,

250
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:37,000
before a job,

251
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:39,920
it's not a good idea to drink Calming Tea.

252
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:03,640
You can do it!
